I've resolved my issue. I've looked through all spring initialization warnings and noticed that my `@Bean(name = "sAMLBootstrap")
  public static SAMLBootstrap sAMLBootstrap()
  {
    return new SAMLBootstrap();
  }` was no declared as `static` and spring was warning me about it or dependencies will not be available for autowiring. After adding static exception related to `ObjectPostProcessor` gone.

